    Package Description
    org.phantomapi
    Contains the base Phantom class which is very useful
    org.phantomapi.async
    Offers powerful async utilities for simple workers or multithreading
    org.phantomapi.clust
    Contains a rubust, powerful configuration and key value data storage system
    org.phantomapi.command
    Contains a command system built on it's own for ease of use
    org.phantomapi.construct
    Used for constructing structured plugins
    org.phantomapi.core
    The core set of controllers phantom uses to host the framework
    org.phantomapi.entity
    Contains entity wrappers for complex tasks other utils may execute
    org.phantomapi.event
    Events phantom has added to bukkits event system
    org.phantomapi.filesystem
    Filesystem utilities such as archiving along with abstracts for new type
    org.phantomapi.game
    Full game api system
    org.phantomapi.gui
    Full, robust gui api using inventories.
    org.phantomapi.hud
    Create gui applications from the running jvm
    org.phantomapi.inventory
    Inventory wrappers used for the stack api along with other utils
    org.phantomapi.lang
    Many objects for holding data in faster, easier ways.
    org.phantomapi.multiblock
    Used for multiblock structures
    org.phantomapi.network
    The network api used for bungeecord networking
    org.phantomapi.nms
    NMS wrappers and packet related methods (NMSX)
    org.phantomapi.physics
    Pure math physics for gravitational/velocity purposes
    org.phantomapi.queue
    Used for processing various queues
    org.phantomapi.schematic
    Schematics, Artifacts, Structures.
    org.phantomapi.sfx
    Audio, Sound structures and distorters.
    org.phantomapi.slate
    Slate api used for tablists and even placeholder tablists
    org.phantomapi.stack
    Stackapi for using a force-set no cloning system for item stacks and inventories
    org.phantomapi.text
    Formatted text, Raw Text, Message builders, Tabulators and more.
    org.phantomapi.util
    The most useful package.
    org.phantomapi.vfx
    Visual effects, particle builders, and particle manipulators/distortions
    org.phantomapi.world
    World wrappers, async utilities, object representations and so much more.
    org.phantomapi.wraith
    Wraith npc's for simple or advanced interaction with players
